&lt;h1 id="be-good"&gt;Be Good&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;April 2008&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;(This essay is derived from a talk at the 2008 Startup School.)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;About a month after we started Y Combinator we came up with the phrase that became our motto: Make something people want. We&amp;rsquo;ve learned a lot since then, but if I were choosing now that&amp;rsquo;s still the one I&amp;rsquo;d pick.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>